OL,3,CChildren's chemotherapy sessions
OL,4,Cdelayed because of staff absences
OL,6,FChildren with cancer are having their
OL,7,Fchemotherapy sessions delayed because
OL,8,Fof staff absences at the Royal Belfast
OL,9,FHospital for Sick Children.
OL,11,FMore than half of its specialist
OL,12,Fcancer nurses are currently off for
OL,13,Fwhat the Belfast Trust says is both
OL,14,Fplanned and unplanned leave.
OL,16,FChair of the Health Committee, Philip
OL,17,FMcGuigan MLA, said: "We're dealing
OL,18,Fwith cancer here. Cancer treatment
OL,19,Fdiagnosis is a time critical issue.
