OL,3,CChildren's chemotherapy sessions
OL,4,Cdelayed because of staff absences
OL,6,F"And also this scenario is around
OL,7,Fchildren, so it's even more important
OL,8,Fthat there can be no delays.
OL,10,F"So I'm very concerned and
OL,11,Fdisappointed to hear that staff
OL,12,Fshortages are impacting on the time
OL,13,Fcritical treatment of cancer,
OL,14,Fparticularly for children, and
OL,15,Fsomething that we need to get to the
OL,16,Fbottom of."
