OL,6,FIn a statement, the Belfast Trust said
OL,7,Fit is "working hard to review all
OL,8,Fnursing roles within the wider
OL,9,Fhematology and oncology departments to
OL,10,Fhelp cover the service".
OL,12,FIt added that the "safety and delivery
OL,13,Fof timely treatment is and will remain
OL,14,Four highest priority".
OL,16,FThe organisation also pointed out that
OL,17,Fall children who require treatment are
OL,18,Fcurrently receiving it.
